ign\">ἡμίονοι ἄ. τανύοντο</foreign> they struggled <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">restlessly</tr_> forwards, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:83\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.83</biblScope> </bibl>: later, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">vehemently, violently,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λὶς ἄ. κεραΐζει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:25:202\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25.202</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">στῆ ῥ) ἄ.</foreign> stood <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">unwaveringly,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:78\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.78</biblScope> </bibl>:—later regul. <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-τως</foreign> Sch.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:410\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.410</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n5450.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> later, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἄμοτος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">furious, savage,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κακόν</foreign> prob. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0261.tlg001:37:16\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bi